                  <td>$50.00</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <p>Note: Fees automatically increase each January based on the Consumer Price Index for the Toronto area.</p>

          <h3>Application Requirements</h3>
          <p>To apply for an STR Host license in Brampton, you must provide:</p>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>Completed application form</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Declaration</strong> that the property is your principal residence</li>
            <li><strong>Floor plan</strong> showing rental areas and square footage</li>
            <li><strong>Proof of ownership</strong> or landlord consent (if tenant)</li>
            <li><strong>License fee</strong> ($150.00)</li>
            <li><strong>Proof of insurance</strong> ($2M liability)</li>
            <li><strong>Criminal record check</strong> (no convictions within 3 years)</li>
            <li><strong>Guest information package</strong> including emergency contacts, fire safety, parking, and waste disposal info</li>
          </ol>

          <div class="callout">
            <div class="callout-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
